<item>
            <title>[LU-14506] lhsmtool_posix uses invalid default values for import</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14506</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When lhsmtool_posix calls &lt;tt&gt;llapi_hsm_import()&lt;/tt&gt;, it passes a stripe offset of 0 which is intended to mean &quot;use the default stripe offset&quot;. But 0 is a valid stripe offset and we should be passing -1 to do what we mean.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
